caption.text:
if you know you know 🥹 thankful my friends are always down to take pictures anyways 
@anzanirestaurant 

Congratulations to @vernoncarandang @mmarkrivera of @drinksula and @victoriaamoreschocolate for an exceptional chocolate and wine tasting event! Your exquisite pairings showcased the perfect harmony between fine chocolate and wine, leaving a lasting impression on all who attended. A heartfelt thank you to @kate8anzani for hosting us in such a beautiful and welcoming setting. Your hospitality truly enhanced the experience, making it a memorable occasion for everyone.
